<typeStatus box="[296,394,388,410]" pageId="53" pageNumber="53">holotype</typeStatus>
in the original description and (
<bibRefCitation author="Chapman, F. M." box="[235,480,417,439]" pageId="53" pageNumber="53" pagination="243 - 278" refId="ref92933" refString="Chapman, F. M. 1923 b. Mutation among birds in the genus Buarremon. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History 48 (9): 243 - 278." type="journal article" year="1923">Chapman, 1923b: 278</bibRefCitation>
