<specimenCount pageId="53" pageNumber="53" type="generic">eight specimens</specimenCount>
he examined, including the type. The 
<specimenCount box="[128,306,476,497]" pageId="53" pageNumber="53" type="generic" typeStatus="paratypes">seven paratypes</specimenCount>
are all from the type locality: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[128,596,505,526]" pageId="53" pageNumber="53">AMNH 139749, 139750, 139752–139756</emphasis>
, 
<specimenCount pageId="53" pageNumber="53" type="male">one male</specimenCount>
, 
<specimenCount box="[198,339,534,556]" pageId="53" pageNumber="53" type="female">five females</specimenCount>
